oared through the L.A. skies and past the Hollywood sign, which had been modified to turn the two \\\"O\\\"s in \\\"wood\\\" into two of the five Olympic rings.\", \"from\": 1099, \"to\": 1311, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1181, \"end\": 1185, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999980669284053, \"rank\": 1.0630303889107706e-06, \"text\": \"L.A.\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}, {\"begin\": 1205, \"end\": 1219, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hollywood sign\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cruise has long been famous for doing extreme stunts for several of his action films, many of which have never been achieved or attempted before.\", \"from\": 1313, \"to\": 1458, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In June 2023, Cruise spoke with ET while in Rome promotingMission: Impossible - Dead Reckoning Part One,and he revealed that themost dangerous stunt of his career-- a motorcycle jump off of a cliff into a base jump -- was the first-ever scene filmed for the action flick.\", \"from\": 1460, \"to\": 1731, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1504, \"end\": 1508, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rome\", \"score\": 0.8830967261682517, \"rank\": 0.13150205598775078, \"text\": \"Rome\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rome\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rome\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Well, we know either we are gonna continue with the film or we are not,\\\" Cruise said with a laugh of planning the death-defying stunt.\", \"from\": 1733, \"to\": 1868, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Let us know day one... Do we all continue, or is it a major rewrite?\\\"\", \"from\": 1869, \"to\": 1939, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In all seriousness, the actor added, it all came down to focus.\", \"from\": 1941, \"to\": 2004, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was years preparing.\", \"from\": 2005, \"to\": 2029, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I mean, I have been riding motorcycles since I was a little kid, raced cars and spent a lot of time just with aerobatics, airplanes, helicopters and parachutes...\", \"from\": 2030, \"to\": 2192, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It all kind of came to that moment,\\\" he explained.\", \"from\": 2193, \"to\": 2243, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You have to be razor sharp when you do something like that, so it was very important as we were prepping the film that that actually was the first thing [to shoot], because I do not want to drop that and go shoot other things and then have my mind somewhere else,\\\" he continued.\", \"from\": 2245, \"to\": 2524, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Everyone was prepped, let us just get it done.\\\"\", \"from\": 2525, \"to\": 2573, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"RELATED CONTENT:  Video  News  News  News  News  News\", \"from\": 2575, \"to\": 2628, \"entities\": []}]}"